      "span_text": "In addition, new methodological approaches regarding the proof of effectiveness in clinical practice are urgently needed [CITATION_1] , last but not least, with a special reference about the much controversial occurrence of a transient effectiveness of lithium even in those cases who originally achieved maintenance while exposed (also) to such drug [7 -9] ."
